urdu transliteration text:
kehdo hawaaon se aahista aayeinkehdo parindon se ghul na machaayeinkehdo andheron se waapas na jayein jaagi huwi chain kuch paa rahi hai
Tell the wind to blow gently,
@HujjatELC

Shayed Rasan ki Aziyat Howi kam,Madham karo Bibion shoor-e-Matam,Sajjad Zanjir Boley na is dam,Shayed Ghamo ki Ghari Jarahi hai,
Ladies please do not cry & do maatam too loudly,
@HujjatELC
